Create Chat Message
POST /api/chatroomchats
Content-Type: application/json
{
  "ChatID": 1,
  "ChatRoomID": 1,
  "StudentID": 5,
  "Body": "Does anyone understand the assignment requirements?",
  "LearningMaterialID": null,
  "CreatedAt": "2025-09-09T14:00:00Z"
}

Get All Chat Messages
GET /api/chatroomchats

Get Chat Message by ID
GET /api/chatroomchats/1

Update Chat Message
PUT /api/chatroomchats/1
Content-Type: application/json
{
  "Body": "I think the assignment is about REST API design.",
  "LearningMaterialID": 3
}

Delete Chat Message
DELETE /api/chatroomchats/1